import * as React from 'react' import './pageSeven.css' import Title from './components/title_bar' import Navbar from './components/nav_bar' import Font from './components/fnt_sze' export default function Imprint(){ const [Lang,SetLang]=React.useState('EN') let LangEN,LangDE; if(Lang === 'EN'){ LangEN = 'block' LangDE = 'none' } else if (Lang === 'DE'){ LangDE='block' LangEN='none' } const [Fntsze,SetFntsze]=React.useState(20) return(
<Navbar onUpdate = {(value:string)=>SetLang(value)}/> <div className = "txt_box"> <h1 style={{display:LangEN}}>Imprint</h1> <h1 style={{display:LangDE}}>Impressum</h1> <Font fntSlct={(sze:number)=>SetFntsze(sze)}/> <hr></hr> <p className = 'para_a' style={{display:LangEN, fontSize:Fntsze}}> <b>Declarations according to § 5 TMG</b> <br></br> <br></br> Internationaler Club Jülich e.V. <br></br> <br></br> Registered in the register of associations, city of Jülich, VR 227 <br></br> <br></br> <b>Postal address:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Münchenerstraße - 4, <br></br> <br></br> 52428, Jülich <br></br> <br></br> E-Mail: info@int-club-juelich.de <br></br> <br></br> <b>Represented by:</b> </p> <p className = 'para_a' style={{display:LangDE, fontSize:Fntsze}}> <b>Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Internationaler Club e.V. <br></br> <br></br> Eingetragen im Vereinsregister der Stadt Jülich, VR 227 <br></br> <br></br> <b>Postal address:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Münchenerstraße - 4, <br></br> <br></br> 52428, Jülich <br></br> <br></br> E-Mail: info@int-club-juelich.de <br></br> <br></br> <b>Represented by:</b> </p> <div className = 'grd_cont' style={{fontSize:Fntsze}}> <div>Ms. Myriam Woischnick-De Buck</div> <div>President</div> <div>Mr. Rolf Skowronek</div> <div>Vice-President</div> <div>Ms. Helga Neulen</div> <div>Treasurer</div> <div>Ms. Rajalekshmi Deepu</div> <div>Secretary</div> <div>Ms. Lorraine Buchner</div> <div>Committee member</div> <div>Ms. Nathalia Faley</div> <div>Committee member</div> <div>Ms. Brunhilde Hütten</div> <div>Committee member</div> <div>Ms. Barbara Kobertz</div> <div>Committee member</div> <div>Ms. Karina Minkenberg</div> <div>Committee member</div> <div>Ms. Georg Neulen</div> <div>Committee member</div> </div> <p className='para_b' style={{fontSize:Fntsze}}> <b>Translations:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Ms. Kay Stone, Ms. Claudia Prell-Zander <br></br> <br></br> <b>Logo:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Barbara Kobertz <br></br> <br></br> <b>Articles:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Ms. Brenda Robson-Eifler, Hans Georg Plott, u. a. <br></br> <br></br> <b>Disclaimer:</b> <br></br> <br></br> We assume no responsibility and/or liability towards the completeness and accuracy of the provided contents. <br></br> <br></br> <b>Data protection:</b> <br></br> <br></br> Further information on our data protection procedures can be found at: <br></br> <br></br> The imprint was created using the imprint generator from <a href = "https://www.activemind.de/datenschutz/generatoren/impressum/" >activeMind AG</a> </p> </div> </div> ) }
